##Data Import Section

read_file -type verilog /data/project/DEU/rtl/sliv_decoder.v
read_file -type verilog /data/project/DEU/rtl/decomp_square.v
read_file -type verilog /data/project/DEU/rtl/compare_swap.v
read_file -type verilog /data/project/DEU/rtl/bitonic_sort.v
